Title: 1. People
Write-Up Text: Despite my efforts to summarize the given posts some of them didn't contain enough information to extract useful insights. However the ones that did highlighted issues such as the flawed gas tax system in Australia frustration within the Liberal Party over costly renovations to the Parliament building and calls for reform to be included in the upcoming budget. While some individuals tagged in the posts could be seen as interesting the lack of context surrounding the links made it difficult to identify what if any relevance they had.
